<</if>>

:: Nightmare Alex Rape Finish
<<effects>>

<<if $enemyarousal gte $enemyarousalmax>>
	<<ejaculation>>

	Alex snickers, leaning back. <<He>> soon climbs off the bed and grabs a stray bottle of alcohol from the nightstand. <<He>> pays you no mind while <<he>> downs the bottle.
	<br><br>
	"You stay there and look cute, you hear? Might need you again soon." <<He>> glances back at you with a smirk and leaves you alone on the bed.
	<br><br>
	You don't have the strength to move, nor the will. You curl up on your broken body and end up falling asleep, your body trembling all the while.
<<else>>
	You manage to free yourself from Alex and scramble to the door. It's jammed. <<Hes>> screaming incoherent nonsense. A glass bottle smashes just beside your head as you struggle to open the door.
	<br><br>
