:: Nightmare Alex End
<<effects>>
<<npc Alex>><<person1>>

<<if $phase is 1>>
	You awake, shaking. The memories of the nightmare play repeatedly in your head.<<stress 18>><<trauma 18>><<gggstress>><<gggtrauma>>
	<br><br>
	You slept, but your body and mind feel utterly exhausted.<<tiredness 15>><<gggtiredness>>
	<br><br>
	A door opens somewhere, and you freeze at the sound of Alex's voice. <<He>> seems to be addressing the farm animals. You wait for <<him>> to start marching upstairs, expecting your nightmare to become a reality. When the door shuts once more, you can't help but still feel unnerved.
	<br><br>
	Alex would never hurt you like that, would <<he>>? <<He>> kept you around all this time. If <<he>> hated you, <<he>> would make you leave, right?
<<else>>
	You awake in a cold sweat.<<stress 12>><<trauma 12>><<ggstress>><<ggtrauma>>
	<br><br>
	You feel dizzy. Your body is more tired than it was before you slept.<<tiredness 10>><<ggtiredness>>
	<br><br>
