:: Nightmare Gwylan Wake
<<effects>>
You turn around and run, your eyes closed. You need to be anywhere else. Away from the ocean.
<br><br>

<<if $willpowerSuccess>>
	You hear Gwylan's voice singing to you. You cover your ears. It does nothing to muffle the song, <span class="green">but it keeps you focused</span>. The air rushes by you as water spouts descend, trying to pull you into oblivion. You will them away.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[다음|Nightmare Gwylan End]]>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
	You hear Gwylan's voice singing to you. <<hypnosisText "<span class='red'>Your body turns around on its own.</span>">> Your eyes open. <<Hes>> on every street corner, staring at you with those empty eyes.
	You run right into <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> embrace. A paradox of terror and relief pulls you in opposite directions, as hundreds of Gwylans giggle and drag you back to the docks.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[다음|Nightmare Gwylan 2]]>><<set $phase to "forced">><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	You hear a familiar voice singing to you. <span class="red">It's so sweet, so alluring.</span> You must have turned around without realising it, as you hear your footsteps on wood once more.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[다음|Nightmare Gwylan 2]]>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

