:: Nightmare Gwylan 2
<<effects>>
<<if $phase is "forced">>
	You're dragged onto the dock, innumerable soft hands forcing you to stand. They guide your steps forward, and you're unable to resist, merely a puppet on strings.
	<br><br>

	The other Gwylans all fall apart and rush ahead in ribbons of themselves, joining the one in front of you as the song reaches a crescendo.
<<else>>
	You can hear the <<personsimple>> at the end singing as you approach. The dock seems to be extending as you walk, as <<he>> doesn't seem to be getting any closer.
	<br><br>

	The song is scrambled. The words don't make sense, but you know it's coming to an end. This fills you with dread, but you don't know why.
<</if>>
