:: Nightmare Office
<<effects>><<nightmareStart "office">><<set $location to "office">>

You find yourself thinking about your day as you try to fall asleep. You flip the pillow over to the cold side and shove your arm underneath before closing your eyes.
<br><br>
Your ears ring as if they're muffling your thoughts, and you blink in a vain attempt to shake it away. A strange sense of uncanniness falls over you as you hear the methodical clacking of a keyboard.<<stress 6>><<gstress>>
<br><br>

<<if $nightmaresSeen.includes("office")>>
	You know this place. It isn't real.
	<br><br>
	<<link [[Try to wake up|Nightmare Office Wake]]>><<set $phase to 0>><</link>><<nightmareWakeDifficulty>>
