:: Nightmare Office 2
<<effects>>

"You have an assignment waiting," you hear someone call out from behind a computer.
<br><br>

<<if $phase is 3>>
	You shake yourself from your stupor and report in for your assignment.
	<br><br>
<<else>>
	You have work to do. You can't just slack off like this; you have to do your job.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

A poster sits in front of you. You grab it and trudge along to the copying room. You place the poster on top of the copy machine. You click the button to start it up. Nothing happens.
<br><br>

You take a step back and look at the shredder next to the copying machine. The shredder is on, judging by the soft hum it emits. You glance at the outlets behind the two machines, and sure enough, the shredder is plugged in, while the copier is not.
<br><br>

You wedge yourself between the two machines to reach the outlet, unplugging one and plugging in the other with a swift motion.
<br><br>

As soon as you plug it in, however, you realise that <span class="red">you are stuck.</span>
<br><br>

Someone's coming. You feel a presence looming over you.
<br><br>

<<link [[Stay still|Nightmare Office 3]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
